metadata.name: 2.Magic Turtle
metadata.description:
The Magic Turtle NFT is an homage to the past of Magic.  
The Magic Turtle, specifically the turtle head itself is made from United States Dollar Bills.  The letters in the word �Magic� have been carefully constructed and made from ripped magazine covers from the now out of print MAGIC magazine.  Each NFT is a customized piece of artwork, and part of a collection of 500 unique Magic Turtle NFT's (Non-Fungible Tokens).
